.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: brown, pink, ivory, azure, turquise
There are 5 different nationalities: indonesian, egyptian, chinese, indian, turkish
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-mirinda, fanta, mirinda, juice
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: brownmaster, old-henry, montecristo, davidoff, siglo
5 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, snake, hamster, rabbit
1. the indonesian is the person who likes ivory
2. the swedish is the owner of the snake
3. the egyptian is the person drinking mirinda
4. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes azure
5. the person who likes pink is the person drinking iced-mirinda
6. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the goat
7. the person who likes turquise is the old-henry-smoker
8. the person drinking fanta is in the middle
9. the indian is on the far left
10. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle
11. the owner of the rabbits is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker
12. the brownmaster-smoker is the person drinking hot-chocolate
13. the chinese is the davidoff-smoker
14. the indian is on the left or right of the person who likes brown
15. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking juice

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    turquise	|     brown	|      ivory	|     pink	|     azure	|
| Nationality	|   indian	|    egyptian	|    indonesian	|    chinese	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     turtle	|    rabbit	|     goat	|     hamster	|      snake	|
| Beverage	|    juice	|     mirinda	|     fanta	|    iced-mirinda	|      hot-chocolate	|
| Cigar		|   old-henry	|    siglo	|  montecristo	|    davidoff	|   brownmaster	|
